title: Tahm Kench An Odd Name?
body:
Does anyone agree that Tahm Kench is an odd name?

It might be something to get used to, but it just seems odd.

replies.body: I dont think it is so out of the ordinary. I just feel the big bayou catfish has an accent on his Tom pronunciation.
I wish his name was Toad.
I honesty think those names are fine. Tahm Kench however, just sounds odd. But maybe I got to get used to it.
I don't like Tahm. Kench is fine, though.
